Be able to create a single-select (from a list of choices) custom field that can be applied to many projects.  However, the list of choices for the field should be specific per project.
e.g. Custom field might be called "Error screen".  For PROJECT1, the options might be "Welcome", "Address entry", and "Delete entry".  For PROJECT2, the options might be "Home", "Calculate", "Print", and "Goodbye".
Each choice for any given project should be disable-able (i.e. visible, but no longer choosable), and should be programmatically updatable (add, update, delete, disable, etc) via API (e.g. SOAP or REST).

